    {
      "id": "Q2",
      "type": "single",
      "title": "**冪次法則**：若 $f(x) = x^n$ ($n$ 為實數)，則 $f'(x) = nx^{n-1}$。\n   *整數次方證明*：利用二項式展開，\n   $(x+h)^n - x^n = [x^n + nx^{n-1}h + \\frac{n(n-1)}{2}x^{n-2}h^2 + \\dots] - x^n = h[nx^{n-1} + h(\\dots)]$。\n   除以 $h$ 並令 $h \\to 0$，即得 $nx^{n-1}$。",
      "options": null,
      "answer": "",
      "kp": "",
      "q_vector": [],
      "explanation": ""
    },
